Class ViewClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • classes.PlayerMethods
      • gui.ViewClass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class ViewClass
extends PlayerMethods
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener
    This application is a simple Mp3 player that allows you to open .mp3 files and play them, also features a play, resume and a stop button so that you can pause resume and stop your music.

    2016-10/27
